Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.49,0:04:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 才不是步步
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.34,0:04:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的啊
